{"word":"H3094 - יְהַלֶּלְאֵל - Yᵉhallelʼêl - yeh-hal-lel-ale' - Jehalellel","slug":"H3094","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">יְהַלֶּלְאֵל</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Yᵉhallelʼêl"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>yeh-hal-lel-ale'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Jehalellel"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: <b><he>יהלּלאל</he></b> <p />Transliteration: <b>yehallel'êl</b> <p />Phonetic: <b>yeh-hal-lel-ale'</b> <p class=\"bdb_def\"><b>BDB Definition</b>:</p> Jehaleleel or Jehalelel = \"God is praised\" <ol><li>a Calebite descendant of Judah</li><li>father of Azariah and a Merarite Levite in the time of Hezekiah</li></ol> <p />Origin: from <a href=\"#/H1984\">H1984</a> and <a href=\"#/H410\">H410</a> <p />TWOT entry: None <p />Part(s) of speech: Proper Name Masculine "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1947\">H1947</a>, <a href=\"#/H1948\">H1948</a>, <a href=\"#/H1974\">H1974</a>, <a href=\"#/H1984\">H1984</a>, <a href=\"#/H1985\">H1985</a>, <a href=\"#/H4110\">H4110</a>, <a href=\"#/H4111\">H4111</a>, <a href=\"#/H8416\">H8416</a>"}]}